The 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics are less than a month away. As athletes prepare for the Games, organizers in China are also preparing for a possible weather emergency. One solution involves a type of Utility Terrain Vehicle (UTV) provided by Chongqing Jialing Special Equipment Co. for the Games. The UTV manufactured by the Chongqing-based company runs like a car, but it's able to operate not only on bumpy roads but in jungles, deserts and snowfields.